body:
## Changes:

 * readded the SPS claim ability
 * All processes are working fine now.
Added ability to claim season chest

* Dashboard works 
 * Improved stability
 * The App is getting bot details on start

* Renting card to reach bronze 2 works
* Dashboard in progress works but progress bar does not update
* I have started to think about adding statistics, maybe in next release

Important changes:
 * add new dashboard using console based ui 
 *  added configurable dec limit

* Ability to claim quest reward chest and report it in UI
 * Console output has been rewritten to make the migration to new Console UI easier as a result it looks different
 * Improved claiming process
 * Renamed the repository so the url is different but name is better

# Changes 
 * SPS and DEC  transfer to user happen before the donation 
 * Added a little breaks betwen SPS transfer to remove the possible error. 
 * Added code guard so the failure in sps/dec trasnfer will not break the process

First release, it should transfer dec, sps and  card from accounts to main account.

UI is still simple I have a branch on which I am creating a nice console UI with configuration. 

Please be aware there could be some bugs still.
